Title: Polar Tee - Roald Amundsen
Body (HTML): <sections><section id="1"><sectionTitle>Details</sectionTitle><sectionBody>Roald Amundsen Tribute T shirt Roald Engelbregt Gravning Amundsen was a Norwegian explorer of polar regions and a key figure of the Heroic Age of Antarctic Exploration He led the first expedition to traverse the Northwest Passage by sea from 1903 to 1906 and the first expedition to the South Pole in 1911 Roald is an ancestor of a founding member of Coalatree so we made this tee shirt to pay tribute to Roald s legacy Classic fit made from 100 Organic recycled cotton</sectionBody></section><section id="2"><sectionTitle>Size &amp; Fit</sectionTitle><sectionBody>Click buy for more sizing information.</sectionBody></section><section id="3"><sectionTitle>Shipping &amp; Returns</sectionTitle><sectionBody>For any exchanges or returns we offer a 30 day return policy on unopened and unworn products.
